snippet.title: The Fazbear Facility X Fangame Direct - Promotional Trailer 2
snippet.description:
"You have no idea what you started..."
- This is your reminder that The Fazbear Facility's Official Trailer premieres during #FangameDirect2
https://gamejolt.com/games/TheFazbearFacility/708822

- Visit the Fangame Direct channel on the official FNaF community tab to see which other fangames will be featured in the event:
https://gamejolt.com/c/fnaf/fangame_direct

- You can also visit the Fangame Direct's Twitter, Youtube, and Gamejolt channels to stay up to date on the event and when it premieres.
